This paper is primarily focused on solving differential equations associated with conservation laws, which is a major branch in computational mathematics. The paper proposes a novel approach using deep reinforcement learning to solve 1-dimensional scalar conservation laws. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.NA (Numerical Analysis), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.SI (Systems and Control), and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
